OL,3,CAnglian Water to pay out #62.8m after
OL,4,Cwastewater failures
OL,6,FThe water regulator has told Anglian
OL,7,FWater to pay out a #62.8 million
OL,8,Fenforcement package due to failures
OL,9,Fmanaging its wastewater treatment
OL,10,Fworks and network.
OL,12,FOfwat said it is proposing that the
OL,13,Fpackage must be paid by the company
OL,14,Fand its shareholders "for the benefit
OL,15,Fof the environment and their
OL,16,Fcustomers".
OL,18,FIt said failures by the company led to
OL,19,F"excessive spills from storm
OL,20,Foverflows".
