OL,3,CAnglian Water to pay out #62.8m after
OL,4,Cwastewater failures
OL,6,FThe industry regulator said its
OL,7,Finvestigation found that the water
OL,8,Ffirm failed to run, maintain and
OL,9,Fupgrade its wastewater operations
OL,10,Fadequately to ensure they could cope
OL,11,Fwith the flows of sewage and
OL,12,Fwastewater coming to them.
OL,14,FIt added that the firm failed to have
OL,15,Fadequate processes and oversight from
OL,16,Fsenior management and its board to
OL,17,Fensure its operations were performing
OL,18,Fproperly and would meet legal
OL,19,Frequirements.
