OL,3,CAnglian Water to pay out #62.8m after
OL,4,Cwastewater failures
OL,6,FLynn Parker, senior director for
OL,7,Fenforcement at Ofwat, said: "Our
OL,8,Finvestigation has found failures in
OL,9,Fhow Anglian Water has operated and
OL,10,Fmaintained its sewage works and
OL,11,Fnetworks, which has resulted in
OL,12,Fexcessive spills from storm overflows.
OL,13,FThis is a serious breach and is
OL,14,Funacceptable.
OL,16,F"We understand that the public wants
OL,17,Fto see transformative change. That is
OL,18,Fwhy we are prioritising this sector-
OL,19,Fwide investigation which is holding
OL,20,Fwastewater companies to account for
OL,21,Fidentified failures.
