OL,3,CAnglian Water to pay out #62.8m after
OL,4,Cwastewater failures
OL,6,F"We are pleased Anglian Water has
OL,7,Faccepted that it got things wrong and
OL,8,Fis now focusing on putting that right
OL,9,Fand taking action to come back into
OL,10,Fcompliance."
OL,12,FThe regulator said Anglian will create
OL,13,Fa #5.8 million community fund to
OL,14,Fsupport projects delivering
OL,15,Fenvironmental and social benefits for
OL,16,Flocal communities, focusing on the
OL,17,Fwater environment.
