OL,3,CAnglian Water to pay out #62.8m after
OL,4,Cwastewater failures
OL,6,FAnglian will also invest #57 million
OL,7,Finto developing excess flow management
OL,8,Fplans to adequately deal with
OL,9,Fwastewater flows in at least eight
OL,10,Fcatchments in its region to provide
OL,11,Flocal environmental improvements.
OL,13,FThe utilities firm, which provides
OL,14,Fservices to seven million people in
OL,15,Fthe east of England, said it would
OL,16,Falso accelerate a number of
OL,17,Finvestments to drive the early
OL,18,Fdelivery of more storm tanks and
OL,19,Fscreens.
