OL,3,CAnglian Water to pay out #62.8m after
OL,4,Cwastewater failures
OL,6,FEarlier this year, Anglian said it was
OL,7,Fputting up bills by 19%, to an average
OL,8,Fof #626 a year, for the 2025/26
OL,9,Ffinancial year from April.
OL,11,FIn May, the water supplier was fined a
OL,12,Frecord #1.42 million for drinking
OL,13,Fwater failures that affected around
OL,14,F1.3 million people.
